## Features of the site 
  - Log in
  - Log out
  -	Forgot password
  - Dashboard
  - Manage product catalog
    - Show list
    - Add category
    - Update catalog
    - Delete category
  -	Product Management
    - Display product list
    - Show product details
    - Filter products
    - More products
    - Product updates
    - Product cloning
    - Delete product
    - Manage product reviews
  - Order management
    - Display order list
    - View order details
    - Update order status
  - Manage articles
    - Show list of articles
    - Show article details
    - Add new articles
    - Duplicate articles
    - Update articles
    - Delete posts
    - Manage comments
  - Feedback management
    - Show response list
    - View feedback details
    - Delete feedback
  -	Manage member
    - Display the list of member accounts
    - Add new members (add employee accounts, user accounts)
    - Update personal information for members
    - Update passwords for employees
    - Lock member account